{
    "type": "script",
    "id": "6185d778-04a6-4b60-928c-ae3e0fa35454",
    "name": "Magic Class Session 1 03 Sense Magic",
    "sceneId": "981d126b-abc7-430a-abb4-e912340c59e6",
    "trigger": {
        "type": "triggers.manual",
        "name": "Manual"
    },
    "entryPoints": [
        {
            "type": "scripts.entryPoint",
            "id": "69e2b252-a1e6-4395-a78b-120c70ed19b7",
            "name": "Main",
            "nodes": [
                {
                    "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                    "id": "ea36e3a0-c382-457b-91e4-dfc6c206d79d",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "amount": "3",
                    "change": "1",
                    "notify": true
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "d198bb19-8878-4d91-89cb-0a93ad7c2d94",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "Today, you will have the marvelous opportunity to learn your very first magical spell - Isn't that exciting?",
                    "emotion": "1",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "c85e27d2-16d0-4a9d-ac3a-942aa11ed44d",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "This spell is called, \"Sense Magic.\" It will allow you to perceive the magical aura that radiates from items infused with magic, magical creatures, or from spells.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "61ffed30-3f9e-4f2f-853c-1ee87cbf5657",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "In addition, Sense Magic will give you some information on the type of magic and whether it is potentially harmful. It can be used to locate hidden magical items and invisible objects.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "2c28516d-7022-493b-a616-3afddc42ba88",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "It is a very practical spell and one that you all should be able to master, even with your limited skill potential.",
                    "emotion": "1",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "f048d40c-cc18-430d-9ed2-8ef0b6cf3fe1",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "Are there any questions before we get started?",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "id": "3dc1fe3d-c047-47cf-b338-865f82c7b6a0",
                    "type": "nodes.improveSkill",
                    "skill": "Magic",
                    "amount": "2",
                    "notify": true
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.showMenu",
                    "id": "973db4f9-c0f7-4781-8127-537728676760",
                    "options": [
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "b0fcb69f-63c4-4172-99f5-7c3035337949",
                            "text": "Ask About Becoming a Wizard",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "8d42d201-9b22-4a4a-ae05-7537ebaaa3fe",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "text": "If we really practice a lot by casting spells and learning magic, could we eventually be skilled enough to become great and powerful Wizards like you?",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "9bcfffa1-51cd-4aa0-8d30-98ba9620a0a5",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "I'm so sorry, but unfortunately even if you develop your Magic skill to the best of your ability, you will merely be a competent Magic-User rather than a Wizard. ",
                                    "emotion": "2",
                                    "emotion2": "4",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "f8d257c4-a11c-40c9-90ab-19908858355d",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "Wizardry requires a combination of Magic, Intelligence, and Will. It also requires a strong personality with the abilities to memorize, visualize, and manifest Magic.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "8fe10990-7261-4c6d-a9fe-26ca2c24d0cb",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "In short, some people are innately drawn to Wizardry. Even then, it requires years of study and practice before one is a true Wizard.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "id": "c4ad46c2-38d3-40ab-8a0c-515bdb0c76da",
                                    "type": "nodes.skillBranch",
                                    "skill": "Charm",
                                    "target": "27",
                                    "success": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "failure": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "notify": true
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                    "id": "124a17ef-e073-4c34-9158-ddb0508185e7",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "amount": "2",
                                    "change": "1",
                                    "notify": true
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "8",
                            "ExitMenu": true
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "28c08146-350c-4625-be72-4493d74be91e",
                            "text": "Ask About Using Sense Magic",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "8408cb6c-da96-4921-bc94-526437556361",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "text": "Can we use Sense Magic to detect hidden doors in the castle?",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "c762ceb3-ec80-4768-934c-702e7ae43599",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "Generally speaking, unless a door is concealed by magic rather than by clever artifice, Sense Magic is rather useless for that purpose. On the other hand, it can detect whether a door or item uses a magical trap.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "id": "9a364643-1229-41eb-ba2c-ab6e50f5c3e3",
                                    "type": "nodes.skillBranch",
                                    "skill": "Smarts",
                                    "target": "27",
                                    "success": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "failure": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "notify": true
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                    "id": "61bb9a9e-fcd9-4a11-82c6-9e993c8f3641",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "amount": "2",
                                    "change": "1",
                                    "notify": true
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "4",
                            "ExitMenu": true
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "5ccbcc9c-d71d-4eb2-a521-bebb905ee238",
                            "text": "Say Something Snarky About Sense Magic",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "842ff1ee-c1e0-47a9-8f53-0c6e69f17c7d",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "text": "So let me get this straight... if we see a mysterious glowing area, we'll be able to tell whether or not it is magical?",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "673f3dbd-2477-41aa-acf5-8f5ebb667e79",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "Indeed you shall! You will also be able to tell if the glow is purposed for lighting an area or to explode upon contact.",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "9b7a60b6-1e05-4cae-9791-e6e8fa69dbeb",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "text": "Ah, with Sense Magic, we will learn if it is a Light Site or a Doom Room?",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "3e586ea0-86d9-4027-ab83-e56261e32109",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "Precisely.",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "id": "a4c54e3b-8edc-48fa-bc33-c4381631f040",
                                    "type": "nodes.skillBranch",
                                    "skill": "Moxie",
                                    "target": "27",
                                    "success": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": [
                                            {
                                                "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                                "id": "e1a05b10-c1c4-47b2-9594-1aaedd657aa9",
                                                "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                                "amount": "2",
                                                "change": "1",
                                                "notify": true
                                            }
                                        ]
                                    },
                                    "failure": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": [
                                            {
                                                "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                                "id": "3abb5889-f4db-40a8-b4b9-c84d276c036a",
                                                "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                                "amount": "1",
                                                "change": "0",
                                                "notify": true
                                            }
                                        ]
                                    },
                                    "notify": true
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "5",
                            "ExitMenu": true
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "1a235246-6fb5-4220-b91e-3d8a89bd4435",
                            "text": "Say Nothing",
                            "nodes": [],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": 0,
                            "ExitMenu": true
                        }
                    ],
                    "AutoAddDone": false,
                    "Unique": false
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "190d4206-ce8a-4ac0-bf24-781d27724e2f",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "Now we will first learn the rune symbol for \"Magic\" and the rune symbol for \"Perceive.\" Next we will combine the two symbols to create the Sense Magic rune.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "b19ffb14-59d0-47ec-82d3-bf721f43b020",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "Then we will learn to visualize them combined together in our minds. When we concentrate upon the Sense Magic rune, it allows us to perceive the magical aura of something close at hand.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "082db205-2ea5-4079-adf0-82eba7ce4054",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "The higher your magical skill, the more you will be able to detect from the spell. Now, let us get started...",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.changeTags",
                    "id": "bcb36fec-a41a-4296-a9f7-63cb99268a94",
                    "scope": "actor",
                    "scopeId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                    "scopeFilterId": null,
                    "tagsToAdd": "SenseMagic",
                    "tagsToRemove": null
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.addJournalEntry",
                    "id": "3ab4f477-f689-4a9b-8b24-8675786fb0ab",
                    "name": "Magic Class Real Magic!",
                    "notify": true,
                    "description": "In today's class, I learned about runes and how to cast spells. If I visualize the combined runes of Magic and Perception, I can cast the \"Sense Magic\" spell. How about that? I'm now a Magic User! "
                }
            ]
        }
